AB_TITLE: Spatiality in Audio Data Emotional Recognition and Dimensionality Reduction using AIFDR
AB_CONTENT: We are from the R&D Department of SIN Education and Technologies and we are pleased to introduce our new algorithm for Dimensionality Reduction named as AIFDR (Audio Inference and Frequency Dimensionality reduction) In this algorithm what we are going to do is. Sparsing the user given data into n_components using (LPMR) and (LPAR) (Linear Propagated Max Reduction) (Linear Propagated Average Reduction.
AB_KEYWORDS: Audio Processing, Machine Learning, Deep learning, Artificial Intellegence
